modName: Warrior Champion Armor from Dragon Age 2
summary: Mix the cool dragon age champion armor with the open and wonderful world of Skyrim!
descriptionHtml: Well, this mod adds the awesome Champion armor from Dragon Age 2 to the world of Skyrim. It is one armor piece and covers except body also arms and legs. I have found that the armor works and looks great with Cloaks of Skyrim and Bandolier - Bags and Pouches. Have fun and enjoy this great armor piece.
author: Unknown
